    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/f2c72b86c33739d20f33fbbc93d7a9c8.poster.avif?t=1771462092\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/f2c72b86c33739d20f33fbbc93d7a9c8.webm?t=1771462092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款节奏感十足的混沌街机射击游戏中彻底狂欢吧！在那些疯狂的派对中尽情舞动、战斗、大笑，<strong>死守跳舞毯就是获胜的唯一法则</strong>。支持多达12名玩家同场竞技，你甚至还能通过<strong>Steam创意工坊音乐包</strong>来自定义你的专属背景音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/00204e6e7b6fbf39e6913746b2b3d07c.poster.avif?t=1771462092\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/00204e6e7b6fbf39e6913746b2b3d07c.webm?t=1771462092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节奏就是一切。跳上踏板，跟上节拍，看着你的分数狂飙——但别高兴得太早，活下来才是硬道理。<strong>跳舞毯每一轮都会吐出全新的强化道具</strong>，从追踪导弹到扭曲时间的陷阱，这绝对是一场无法预测的音乐大乱斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/4c72defb9d4cdc4ae7831b62ff558600.poster.avif?t=1771462092\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/4c72defb9d4cdc4ae7831b62ff558600.webm?t=1771462092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和哥们儿开个<strong>私人房间</strong>，或者直接加入<strong>公共派对</strong>与全球玩家一决高下！<strong>实时语音</strong>让派对气氛始终火热，你可以一边飞掷香蕉，一边为了节奏大打出手。<strong>游戏模式包括：</strong>乱斗、组队、感染、推车、香蕉争夺战以及猿猴军械库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/22546f686494e9fc11848f515a17f1ba.poster.avif?t=1771462092\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217900/extras/22546f686494e9fc11848f515a17f1ba.webm?t=1771462092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在风格迥异的野外竞技场中战斗——从海盗湾、荒漠台地到辐射小镇和太空站俱乐部。<strong>每个关卡都有独特的惊喜、障碍和战术策略</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关注我们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想知道下一步动向吗？在社交媒体上关注我们，获取最新资讯、独家情报和更多大猩猩表情包。<strong>你绝对不想错过这场派对！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
